title: Test
summary: This grouped bar chart has 3 categories of Fiber Type on the x axis representing 10 groups: 2000, 2010, 2011, 2012, 2013, 2014, 2015, 2016, 2017, and 2018.
Averaging these 10 groups, the highest category is found for Fiber Type Total with a mean value of 59594.0.
Followed by Synthetic fibers with a mean value of 54101.7.
The lowest category is observed at Cellulose fibers that has a mean value of 5492.3
showing a difference of 166.2% with the maximum value.

In case of Total, 2000 shows more dominance than any other Fiber Type and it has the lowest value in Cellulose fibers. On the other hand, group 2010 is the second impactful group in this chart, and it's highest in case of Total and has the minimum dominance for Fiber Type Cellulose fibers.
